                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="https://figure.bohrium.com/400x200/FFFF33/000000?text=Wedding+Photo+2" alt="Wedding Photography Example 2">
                    <h3>Weddings - Ceremony</h3>
                    <p>Every detail, every emotion, preserved beautifully.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="https://figure.bohrium.com/400x200/57FF33/FFFFFF?text=Portrait+Photo+2" alt="Portrait Photography Example 2">
                    <h3>Portraits - Family Session</h3>
                    <p>Timeless memories for families to cherish.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="https://figure.bohrium.com/400x200/5733FF/FFFFFF?text=Event+Photo+2" alt="Event Photography Example 2">
