                    <p>Vibrant and energetic coverage of live performances.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="services" class="container">
            <h2>Services Offered</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">Tailored photography packages to suit your unique needs.</p>

            <div class="services-list">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Wedding Photography</h3>
                    <p>Comprehensive coverage of your wedding day, including pre-wedding shoots, ceremony, reception, and custom albums. Packages start from .</p>
