                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <h3>Event Photography</h3>
                    <p>Professional documentation of corporate events, parties, conferences, and celebrations. Hourly rates available. Please inquire for a custom quote.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Event coverage</li>
                        <li>Candid and posed shots</li>
                        <li>Prompt delivery of images</li>
                        <li>Optional: On-site printing, video services</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Client Testimonials</h2>
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"RS Photography captured our wedding day perfectly. The photos are absolutely stunning, and they were so professional and easy to work with!"</p>
