                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"The portrait session was fantastic! I felt so comfortable, and the final images exceeded my expectations. Highly recommend!"</p>
                    <footer>— Emily R.</footer>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"For our corporate event, RS Photography delivered exceptional results. They captured the energy and importance of the day beautifully."</p>
                    <footer>— Mark T., Event Coordinator</footer>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="container">
            <h2>Contact Me</h2>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Ready to capture your special moments? Get in touch today!</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@rsphotography.com</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (123) 456-7890</p>
                <address>
                    <p><strong>Studio Address:</strong><br>
                    123 Photography Lane<br>
                    Creative City, PC 12345</p>
                </address>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/rsphotography" target="_blank" aria-label="Instagram">📸</a>
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/rsphotography" target="_blank" aria-label="Facebook">👍</a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rsphotography" target="_blank" aria-label="LinkedIn">🔗</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 RS Photography. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
